#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.combine.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.combine"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:1 of
msgid "Perform column-wise combine with another DataFrame."
msgstr "与另一个 DataFrame 进行列式合并。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:3 of
msgid ""
"Combines a DataFrame with `other` DataFrame using `func` to element-wise "
"combine columns. The row and column indexes of the resulting DataFrame "
"will be the union of the two."
msgstr ""
"使用 `func` 对两个 DataFrame 的列进行逐元素合并。结果 DataFrame 的行索引"
"和列索引是两个 DataFrame 的并集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:7 of
msgid "The DataFrame to merge column-wise."
msgstr "要按列合并的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:9 of
msgid ""
"Function that takes two series as inputs and return a Series or a scalar."
" Used to merge the two dataframes column by columns."
msgstr ""
"接受两个 Series 作为输入并返回一个 Series 或标量的函数。用于逐列合并两个 "
"DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:12 of
msgid "The value to fill NaNs with prior to passing any column to the merge func."
msgstr "在将任何列传递给合并函数之前用于填充 NaN 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:15 of
msgid ""
"If True, columns in `self` that do not exist in `other` will be "
"overwritten with NaNs."
msgstr "如果为 True，则 `self` 中不存在于 `other` 的列将被 NaN 覆盖。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:19 of
msgid "Combination of the provided DataFrames."
msgstr "提供的 DataFrame 的合并结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.combine_first`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:25 of
msgid ""
"Combine two DataFrame objects and default to non-null values in frame "
"calling the method."
msgstr "合并两个 DataFrame 对象，默认使用调用该方法的帧中的非空值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:28 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:29 of
msgid "Combine using a simple function that chooses the smaller column."
msgstr "使用选择较小列的简单函数进行合并。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:41 of
msgid "Example using a true element-wise combine function."
msgstr "使用真正的逐元素合并函数的示例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:50 of
msgid ""
"Using `fill_value` fills Nones prior to passing the column to the merge "
"function."
msgstr "使用 `fill_value` 在将列传递给合并函数之前填充空值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:60 of
msgid ""
"However, if the same element in both dataframes is None, that None is "
"preserved"
msgstr "但是，如果两个 DataFrame 中相同位置的元素都是 None，则该 None 会被保留"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:70 of
msgid ""
"Example that demonstrates the use of `overwrite` and behavior when the "
"axis differ between the dataframes."
msgstr "演示 `overwrite` 使用方法以及当 DataFrame 之间轴不同时行为的示例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.df_combine:87 of
msgid "Demonstrating the preference of the passed in dataframe."
msgstr "演示传入的 DataFrame 的优先级。"

